This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-nix layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky
  branch: honister

  URI: https://github.com/openembedded/meta-openembedded.git
  branch: honister

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-nix layer as pull requests on
https://github.com/nwns/meta-nix

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-nix layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-nix layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-nix'

II. Misc
========

NOTE: Currently only Linux x86_64 is supported.

NOTE: This layer installs nix into a baked image by following the process
outlined by the projects installer script as provided on the webserver.
